metadata.name: Lovely date #01 Morning coffee
metadata.description:
Her name is Emilu. This is a special time for her and you. You're drinking morning coffee with her at a cafe. She's so happy to spend time with you.
The winner of the auction will own her.

All bidders will receive an emilu coffee stamp airdrop. The winner of the auction will receive all stamps without bidding when another art is posted on the lovely date collection.
